N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-5.91 - Condenser unit

State Regulations

In vending machines having a condenser unit as an integral part, the condenser unit is to be: (a) separated from the food and container storage space by a dust-proof barrier when located below these spaces; or
(b) sealed from the food and container storage space when located above these spaces. Notes
